org.softsmithy.lib.swing.action

Interface XAction

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Action, ActionListener, EventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractXAction, DefaultXAction, ReflectiveXAction, XActionWrapper

    public interface XAction
extends Action
    XAction extends Action by defining more property keys and convenience methods.
    Note: The API may change in a future version!
    Note: Eventually this belongs to the javax.swing.Action interface.
    Author:
    Florian Brunner
